Dependencies:

- evldns commit b64db4fc8d95b2d5a959c982aa59e6d6fdac35fd or later)
- 'rpb-dev' branch of patched ldns (https://github.com/raybellis/ldns)
- libevent2

To build from Git:

% libtoolize --install
% autoreconf --install
% ./configure --with-ldns=<path...> --with-evldns=<path...>
% make

Zone names, paths, keys, etc, currently hard-coded in each daemon.

Process farm code (process.[ch]) is currently Linux specific due to
use of pthread_set_affinity_np()
